UNITED STATES of America v. J. B. and Beulah PUCKETT. No. 3417. Circuit Court of Appeals, Tenth Circuit. Oct. 7, 1946. Curtis P. Harris, Sp. Atty., Department of Justice, of Oklahoma City, Okl., for appellant. Wise & Ivester, of Sayre, Okl., for ap-pellees.

Before PHILLIPS, Circuit Judge, and SYMES, District Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal docketed and dismissed pursuant to stipulation.
